\c 10 Rudzi rwaAhabhi navaporofita vaBhaari vanoparadzwa 1 Zvino Ahabhi wakanga ana vanakomana vana makumi manomwe paSamaria. Jehu akanyora nwadhi, akadzitumira Samaria kuvabati veJezereri, ivo vakuru, nokuvareri vavana vaAhabhi, akati, 2 "Zvino kana nwadhi iyi ichisvika kwamuri, vanakomana vatenzi wangu zvavariko kwamuri, nengoro namabhiza zviriko kwamuri, neguta rakakombwa norusvingo, nenhumbi dzokurwa nadzo; 3 chizvitsaurirai mwanakomana watenzi wenyu wakaisvonaka wakakwana kukunda vamwe, mumugadze pachigaro choushe chababa vake, murwire imba yatenzi wenyu." 4 Asi ivo vakanga vachitya kwazvo, vakati, "Madzimambo maviri akanga asingagoni kumukunda, zvino isu tichamukunda seiko?" 5 Zvino mutariri weimba nomutariri weguta, navakuru, navareri vavana vakatuma shoko kuna Jehu, vachiti, "Tiri varanda venyu, tichaita zvose zvamunotiraira; hatingagadzi mumwe mambo; itai henyu sezvamunoda." 6 Ipapo wakanyora nwadhi rwechipiri kwavari, akati, "Kana mukanzwana neni, kana mukaterera izwi rangu, uyai kwa ndiri Jezereri mangwana nenguva ino nemisoro yavarume, ivo vanakomana vatenzi wenyu." Zvino vanakomana vamambo, ivo vanhu vana makumi manomwe, vaiva kuvakuru veguta, vaivarera. 7 Zvino nwadhi iyo yakati ichisvika kwavari, vakabata vanakomana vamambo, vakavauraya, ivo vanhu vana makumi manomwe, vakaisa misoro yavo mumatengu, ndokuitumira kwaari Jezereri. 8 Nhume ikasvika, ikamuudza, ikati, "Vauya nemisoro yavanakomana vamambo." Iye akati, "Itai mirwi miviri nayo, muiise pavanopinda napo pasuo, kusvikira mangwana." 9 Fume mangwana akabuda, akandomirapo, akati kuvanhu vose, "Imi hamune mhosva henyu; tarirai, ndini ndamukira tenzi wangu, ndikamuuraya; asi ndianiko auraya ava vose? 10 Zvino muzive kuti hakuna shoko rimwe raJehovha richawira pasi, rakataurwa naJehovha pamusoro peimba yaAhabhi; nokuti Jehovha wakaita zvaakataura nomuranda wake Eria." 11 Naizvozvo Jehu akauraya vose vakanga vasara veimba yaAhabhi paJezereri, navanhu vake vakuru vose, neshamwari dzake, navapristi vake, kusvikira asina kumusiyira nomumwe. 12 Zvino akasimuka, akabva, akaenda Samaria. Wakati asvika paimba yavafudzi panzira, pavaiveura makwai, 13 Jehu akasangana navanun'una vaAhazi mambo waJudha, akati, "Ndimi aniko?" Ivo vakapindura, vakati, "Tiri vanun'una vaAhazia, toburuka kundokwazisa vana vamambo navana vavahosi." 14 Iye akati, "Vabatei vari vapenyu." Vakavabata vari vapenyu, vakavauraya padziva reimba pavaiveura makwai, varume vaiva vana makumi mana navaviri; haana kusiya mumwe wavo. 15 Zvino wakati abvapo, akasangana naJehonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhu, wanga achiuya kuzosangana naye; akamukwazisa, akati kwaari, "Mwoyo wako wakarurama here, sokururama kwomwoyo wangu kwauri?" Jehonadhabhi akapindura, akati, "Wakarurama hawo. Kana zvakadaro, ndibate ruoko -vwaxig,u." Iye akabata ruoko rwake, ndokumukwidza mungoro maakanga ari. 16 Akati, "Hendei, undoona kushingaira kwandinoshingairira Jehovha nako." Naizvozvo vakamufambisa mungoro yake. 17 Wakati asvika Sarnaria, akauraya vose
